metadata.name: Frontline Otter #1
metadata.description:
Inspired by the frontliners during the Covid 19 pandemic, Frontline Otters is a collection of unique NFTs that exist on the Ethereum Blockchain.

As the first ever medical NFT collection, our holders stand to play a part in the history by buying into our project! Be involved by participating in giveaways, contests and more to stand a chance to win free-to-mint otters and other exciting rewards! For more information, visit https://www.frontlineotters.io
